2.  **Getter Hooks:**
    *   **Methods:** `com.huawei.astp.macle.model.log.TempUploadUrlResponseDataHeader.getHost()`, `com.huawei.astp.macle.model.log.TempUploadUrlResponseDataHeader.getContentType()`
    *   **Purpose:** These hooks allow a researcher to observe when the `host` or `contentType` values are accessed by other parts of the application. This helps trace where these network-related details are being consumed (e.g., when constructing an `HttpRequest`).

