    *   **Hooking Setters:** To see or modify mutable time values:
        ```javascript
        Java.perform(function() {
            var PageStartTime = Java.use("com.huawei.astp.macle.model.log.PageStartTime");
            PageStartTime.setEventTime.implementation = function(time) {
                console.log("[Frida] setEventTime() called. Original: " + this.getEventTime() + ", New: " + time);
